dc_description_s: Includes index to some buildings. "M.C." in lower right corner of map. From handbook printed by the Ann Arbor Press. Advertisements on front and verso including Haller the Jeweler, Campus Club, Ann Arbor Press, Marlin Fire Arms, and Sheehan & Co. 1 map; 19 x 19 cm., folded to 13 x 6 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
